'''全國熱狗和香腸協會'''（{{lang-en|'''National Hot Dog and Sausage Council'''}}，簡稱'''NHDSC'''）是一個促進[[熱狗|熱狗]]和[[香腸|香腸]]行業發展的美國商會。<ref>{{cite web|author = Dan Barry|title = Ambassador Hot Dog|work = The New York Times|date = 2006-06-06|url = https://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/07/weekinreview/07barry.html|access-date = 2021-03-29|archive-date = 2021-06-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210623135842/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/07/weekinreview/07barry.html}}}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1129&dat=19980709&id=ubNRAAAAIBAJ&pg=6862,4800886&hl=en |title = Council aims to polish hot dog's image |author = Art Chapman |date = 1998-07-09 |publisher = Fort Worth Star-Telegram |language = en}}</ref>

該協會由{{link-en|美國肉品協會|American Meat Institute}}於1994年成立。它的總部設在[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]，現任主席是艾瑞克·米頓索爾（Eric Mittenthal）。

該協會將每年7月作為「全國熱狗月」（National Hot Dog Month），而「全國熱狗日」（National Hot Dog Day）則根據北美肉品協會在國會山莊舉辦年度熱狗午餐的時間而有所不同。2017年的全國熱狗日是在7月19日的星期三。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/pilot-flying-j-ups-the-ante-for-national-hot-dog-day-with-free-rolling-grill-menu-item-300296473.html |title = Flying J Ups the Ante for National Hot Dog Day |publisher = PRNewswire |language = en |access-date = 2021-03-29 |archive-date = 2018-11-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181122005618/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/pilot-flying-j-ups-the-ante-for-national-hot-dog-day-with-free-rolling-grill-menu-item-300296473.html }}</ref>同樣，它也宣傳10月為「全國香腸月」（National Sausage Month）。

2015年11月，NHDSC在熱狗是否符合[[三明治|三明治]]的類型這一問題上，發布一項政策來結束爭論，稱熱狗不是三文治。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/07/a-hot-dog-is-not-a-sandwich/75362898/ |title = Is a hot dog a sandwich? Council rules once and for all |author = Lindsay Deutsch |date = 2015-11-07 |publisher = USA TODAY |language = en |access-date = 2021-03-29 |archive-date = 2021-01-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210127234613/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/11/07/a-hot-dog-is-not-a-sandwich/75362898/ }}</ref>其他消息來源反駁這個說法。

2019年，NHDSC任命Tyler Field為他們的終身榮譽主席，以感謝他「不厭其煩地服務於熱狗和那些創造熱狗的人」。

